              <li><a href="#">Ultimate Weapons</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Elemental Tablets Locations</a></li>
            </ul>
          </details>

          <details class="nav-section">
            <summary><h3>Ashes of Elrant DLC</h3></summary>
            <details class="nav-subsection">
              <summary><h4>Introduction</h4></summary>
              <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#">Introduction</a></li>
              </ul>
            </details>

            <details class="nav-subsection">
              <summary><h4>Walkthrough</h4></summary>
              <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#">Into the Unknown</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Beyond the Rift</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">The Big Escape</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">The Truth of Elrant</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">The Open Way</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Final World Exploration</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Deus Ex Machina</a></li>
              </ul>
            </details>

            <details class="nav-subsection">
              <summary><h4>Sidequest</h4></summary>
              <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#">A Second Option</a></li>
              </ul>
            </details>

            <details class="nav-subsection">
              <summary><h4>Reward Board</h4></summary>
              <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#">Mushroom Forest</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Elrant City</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Lost Gardens</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Deadlands</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Wastelands</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Old Town</a></li>
              </ul>
            </details>

            <details class="nav-subsection">
              <summary><h4>Guides</h4></summary>
              <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#">All DLC Class Emblems</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">All DLC Collectibles</a></li>
